  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">217651 Education Cannot Wait (ECW) Burundi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education Cannot Wait as a donor in collaboration with UNICEF have contacted World Burundi to prime for a $12 Million project (Match is optional but highly recommended) The project will be 3 years and will potential be starting in September 2021. Project/program design deadline: we expect the first draft on 15 July . Design team : Mainly made by UNICEF and World Vision plus strategic partner ( Ministry of Education and UNESCO )
 
  
 
 Geographic area will be: 2 provinces (Cibitoke and Makamba ) ; provinces with huge needs in education sector with few partners in education. World Vision has already opened a long-term program in Makamba province and has already 2 grants under implementation. Cibitoke province is also a strategic province where World Vision has already identified in the fragile context programming approach.</narrative>
  </description>
